Episode 4297: Bapuji's Rescue
--------------------------------------------------------
As Bapuji's bluff is exposed by the Pakistani soldiers, he faces a difficult challenge. Will he manage to rescue both himself and the fishermen from this predicament?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Charche - Xvir Grewal & Dhanda Nyoliwala (Music Video) | Deepesh Goyal | VYRL Haryanvi
snippet.description:
Watch the groundbreaking collaboration that brings together the best of Punjab and Haryana in a rap extravaganza as ever rising Dhanda Nyoliwala joins forces with Xvir Grewal for a one-of-a-kind Punjabi-Haryanvi track.

Listen to Charche on:

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/7a3QGSVDPG5NHTXKuZVurS?si=906bc7f0fea446aa
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/charche/1789944518?i=1789944519
JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/charche/XSMAdRlmYgA

Make your reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1864907074313373/

#VYRLHaryanvi #Charche #DhandaNyoliwala 

Audio Credits:
Singer, Lyrics, Composer: Xvir Grewal, Dhanda Nyoliwala
Music: Romeoz
Mix Master: Ashock
Project by: Sumit Bamal

Video Credits:
Director: Deepesh Goyal
DOP: Vikcee
AD: Amit Syal, Ankit Thapa
Editor/DI: Bharat Mittal/Deepesh Goyal
DOP Asst.: Rahul Sabharwal
Operator: Rupi
Asst.: Pawan Kumar
Chief AD: Khyati Sharma
EP: Raja
Line Production: Arman Harutyunan
VFX: KP VFX Studios
CGI/3D: Parryfied
Foley: Apsy Singh
Design: Sumit Bamal

Music release inquiries: contact.vyrlregional@umusic.com 

Lyrics:

Gaddi shookdi hi jaave
Munda 150 te laave
Naal 4 yaar khas
Keda sanu hath laave
Dur bitcha toh snitcha toh
Life sohni saari jaave
Jaan kaala kaala yaara di yaari te karche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche


Baade rooh de rangeen Munde 
Att de shaukeen Munde 
Gaal hove ankhan di
Saade bad scene hunde
Sire de ae dith
Tappe saadi leek
Fer malo mali malo mali malo mali
Sir  chad jaande parche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

Tu beeta hua kal
Mera flow jaise Future 
Underground chalu jaise mein
Mewat ka koi Buchter
Jo bars meri week thi 
Vo tere liye tutor hai 
Tu ankh band kre baitha jaise koi kabootar hai
 Gangster sune mere gaane baithe jail mein
Mein Dm Nahi krta bars karu mail mein
Naam k hi rapper hai yeah sun tu detail mein
Labelo pe dekhe hai zameer inke sale mein
Luck te nahi khade hai hukk the
Mein Fuck na deyu Koi deta jo takht pe
Vakht hai mera inki jamante japt hai
Mere doore Dhari inki amante girvi
Inke pale daale kuch ni 
Yeah baat maare fir bhi
Jind k julane tak
Delhi k buwane tak
Naam le diye tu tanne pahochade tikane tak
Maa duae mere sath hai sath hai 
Oh sikra mein guddi kya baat hai baat hai
Bhai kisse ka digaya nahi digda mein
Jab tak sar pr bhole ka mere hath hai hath hai
Ehna hoya ni siyana 
Har cheez te mein bola
Kaam di ae bukh fame da ni rola
Buss dekhi chalo jatt kidda thal de barola
Jurta naa jande ae takh palte
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche
Obvious ae gaal saade hone charche
Hunda vi ae hone vi ae saade charche
Aam jahi gaal saadi hone charche

snippet.title: Hyundai Creta Electric Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Hyundai is finally launching its new EV, made in India for the Indian market. It will be available in two battery packs and various trims and is expected to start at around Rs 17 Lakh. The top end with 51.4Kwh and ADAS features should cost more than Rs 22 Lakh. I got a chance to drive it recently, and here are my impressions.

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
00:28 Charging
02:01 Exteriors including Key fob, Wheels, Charging port, etc
09:22 Interiors including Infotainment, MID, Steering, seats, etc
20:45 Rear seat space and amenities
22:30 Boot Space
23:30 Drive Impressions on City & Highway roads, including Ride, Dynamics, Handling, Power, ADAS, Regeneration, etc.
36:16 Conclusion 

Download Statiq app: https://bit.ly/3AYuiyQ

snippet.description:

Daya purposefully loses the Antakshari so that everyone can sleep, and Jethalal orders dinner for everyone because they all appear to be hungry. She makes Champaklal and Jethalal proud with this gesture. Later, all of the locals get together at Sodi's house to organize the Gokuldham Society's anniversary.

Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 199
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

snippet.title: Match Highlights | KBFC v OFC | Malayalam | #ISL | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Kerala Blasters'  pursuit for playoffs received a huge boost after a last-gasp win over Odisha FC.


The hosts fell behind early, but surged back before eventually Noah Sadaoui's stoppage-time winner downed Odisha FC 3-2. Jesus Jimenez and Kwame Peprah were the other goal-scorers for the hosts, while Jerry Mawihmingthanga and Dorielton found the back of the net for the Kalinga Warriors.

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat‚Äôs biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti‚Äôs life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat‚Äôs rising career, Shruti‚Äôs failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?

Ayesha Singh as Mannat

snippet.title: First Computer to QUANTUM COMPUTERS - Full Technology Evolution Explained
snippet.description:
Checkout LPU to learn new age skills - https://shorturl.at/VdcQ8 

Research references -  https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FS4NCssJYfQtDOlTsFr1FsLU6dV-D44JCmuwYWOl31k/edit?usp=drivesdk

The fastest supercomputer, El-Capitan, costing ‚Çπ5,000 crores, performs 2 quintillion calculations per second. However, it‚Äôs about to be surpassed. Google‚Äôs Quantum AI Chip "Willow" can process calculations 1 Nonillion (1 followed by 30 zeroes) times faster than today‚Äôs supercomputers. Tasks requiring 500 trillion times the universe's age for completion on current supercomputers can now be done in just 5 minutes. This breakthrough marks the beginning of a quantum computing revolution.
Quantum computing could unlock solutions to the universe‚Äôs deepest mysteries, pinpoint alien life, enable light-speed travel, cure all diseases, extend human life to 150-200 years, and even achieve immortality by uploading consciousness into machines.
However, creating quantum computers as accessible as today‚Äôs systems remains a challenge. Companies like Microsoft, Amazon, IBM, and Intel are working to solve this, but Google‚Äôs innovation puts it ahead in the race. This technology is poised to transform the impossible into reality.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4295 - Bapuji Kyu Ban Gaye Pakistan Jasoos?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
